        "text": "Yes, EmotionEat offers a free plan with 1 emotional check-in per day and weekly pattern analysis. Premium plans offer more check-ins, daily analysis, and personalized grounding strategies for those who want deeper support with anxiety eating."
      }
    }
  ]
};
